<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="A minimal editorial portfolio" />
    <title>Demo 001 — Minimal Editorial</title>
    <style>
      /* Reset & Base */
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #000000;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .font-serif {
        font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
      }

      /* Max-width container */
      .max-w-content {
        max-width: 680px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        padding-right: 1.5rem;
      }

      /* Colors */
      .text-accent { color: #1a3a5c; }
      .text-accent:hover { color: #2a5a8c; }
      .text-gray-400 { color: #9ca3af; }
      .text-gray-500 { color: #6b7280; }
      .text-gray-600 { color: #4b5563; }

      /* Back link */
      .back-link {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.75rem 0;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .back-link:hover { color: #1a3a5c; }

      /* Header */
      header {
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      header nav {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      header .logo {
        font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      header .logo:hover { color: #1a3a5c; }
      header .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        list-style: none;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
      header .nav-links a {
        color: #4b5563;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      header .nav-links a:hover,
      header .nav-links a.active {
        color: #1a3a5c;
      }
      header .nav-links a.active {
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      /* Main content */
      main {
        flex: 1;
        padding-top: 3rem;
        padding-bottom: 3rem;
        width: 100%;
      }

      /* Sections */
      section { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

      /* Intro */
      .intro h1 {
        font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .intro h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
      }
      .intro p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.75;
        max-width: 32rem;
      }

      /* Section header row */
      .section-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        justify-content: space-between;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .section-header h2 {
        font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .section-header a {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #1a3a5c;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .section-header a:hover { color: #2a5a8c; }

      /* Article list */
      .article-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
      .article-item a {
        display: block;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }
      .article-item time {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #9ca3af;
      }
      .article-item h3 {
        font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .article-item:hover h3 { color: #1a3a5c; }
      .article-item p {
        color: #4b5563;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      /* Video embed placeholder */
      .video-embed {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: #9ca3af;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      .video-embed .play-icon {
        width: 3rem;
        height: 3rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #1a3a5c;
        color: #fff;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-right: 0.75rem;
      }
      .video-meta h3 {
        font-family: Georgia, Cambria, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .video-meta p {
        color: #4b5563;
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
      }

      /* Social links grid */
      .social-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      @media (min-width: 640px) {
        .social-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      }
      .social-link {
        display: block;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .social-link:hover {
        border-color: #1a3a5c;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(26, 58, 92, 0.1);
      }
      .social-link .link-name {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .social-link .link-desc {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
      }
      .social-link:hover .link-name { color: #1a3a5c; }

      .see-all-links {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .see-all-links a {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #1a3a5c;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      .see-all-links a:hover { color: #2a5a8c; }

      /* Footer */
      footer {
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }
      footer .footer-inner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      footer .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      footer .footer-links a {
        color: #6b7280;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      footer .footer-links a:hover { color: #1a3a5c; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Back to index -->
    <div class="max-w-content">
      <a href="/site/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to index</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <header>
      <nav class="max-w-content">
        <a href="#" class="logo">Portfolio</a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
          <li><a href="#" class="active">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Articles</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Videos</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Links</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
      <div class="max-w-content">
        <!-- Intro -->
        <section class="intro">
          <h1 class="font-serif">Hello, I'm a creator.</h1>
          <p>
            I write about technology, design, and the things I learn along the way.
            This is my corner of the internet — a place for articles, videos, and
            curated links.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Recent Articles -->
        <section>
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Recent Articles</h2>
            <a href="#">View all &rarr;</a>
          </div>
          <div class="article-list">
            <article class="article-item">
              <a href="#">
                <time>March 28, 2026</time>
                <h3>Building Resilient Design Systems at Scale</h3>
                <p>
                  A practical guide to creating design systems that evolve gracefully
                  as teams grow and requirements shift over time.
                </p>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="article-item">
              <a href="#">
                <time>March 22, 2026</time>
                <h3>The Quiet Power of Minimalism in Web Design</h3>
                <p>
                  Why stripping away the unnecessary leads to stronger
                  communication, better usability, and more memorable experiences.
                </p>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="article-item">
              <a href="#">
                <time>March 15, 2026</time>
                <h3>Typography on the Web: Beyond Google Fonts</h3>
                <p>
                  Exploring self-hosted type, variable fonts, and optical sizing
                  for a more refined reading experience.
                </p>
              </a>
            </article>
            <article class="article-item">
              <a href="#">
                <time>March 8, 2026</time>
                <h3>Rethinking Navigation Patterns for Content Sites</h3>
                <p>
                  How editorial websites can move beyond hamburger menus and embrace
                  navigation that serves readers first.
                </p>
              </a>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Featured Video -->
        <section>
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Featured Video</h2>
            <a href="#">View all &rarr;</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="video-embed">
              <div class="play-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <polygon points="5,3 19,12 5,21" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Video: Designing for Readability</span>
            </div>
            <div class="video-meta">
              <h3>Designing for Readability: A Practical Walkthrough</h3>
              <p>
                A 20-minute deep dive into line height, measure, and contrast ratios
                that make long-form content a pleasure to read.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Social Links -->
        <section>
          <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Find Me Online</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="social-grid">
            <a href="https://github.com" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <div class="link-name">GitHub</div>
              <div class="link-desc">Open source projects and code</div>
            </a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <div class="link-name">LinkedIn</div>
              <div class="link-desc">Professional network and resume</div>
            </a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <div class="link-name">Twitter / X</div>
              <div class="link-desc">Thoughts and conversations</div>
            </a>
            <a href="https://youtube.com" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <div class="link-name">YouTube</div>
              <div class="link-desc">Video tutorials and talks</div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="see-all-links">
            <a href="#">See all links &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <div class="max-w-content footer-inner">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Portfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://github.com">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com">Twitter</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
